    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for razor-sharp throttle response. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and retains factory-spec torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Meticulously maintained with recent rod bearing service and a fresh valve adjustment, this specimen exhibits zero parasitic loss and operates perfectly within original tolerances. It is a concours-level example for the discerning driver who values mechanical purity and peak performance.",
